12. HIV infection;
13. Pregnant and lactating women (pregnancy in this trial is defined as a positive urine or blood pregnancy test);
14. Participation in other drug or medical device clinical trials at present;
15. Alcohol or drug abuse;
16. Lack of compliance with the trial or the ability to sign an informed consent form;
17. Other situations deemed unsuitable for participation in the trial by the investigator.

